text: Pa is a masculine given name, a nickname and a surname. It may refer to: * Edwin "Pa" Watson (1883–1945), United States Army major general, friend and a senior aide to President Franklin D. Roosevelt * Pa Dibba (born 1987), Gambian footballer * Pa Konate (born 1994), Swedish footballer * Pa Laide (), Irish footballer * Pa Odiase (1934–2013), Nigerian composer who wrote his country's national anthem * Pa Socheatvong (born 1957), Cambodian politician, former Governor of Phnom Penh * Sam Pa, pseudonym of a mysterious Chinese businessman Category:Masculine given names
title: Pa (name)
